{"tid":1981304,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"公子講 YouTuber","createTime":"2020-04-20T14:54:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T15:17:46.000Z","uid":165934,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f3c21494ee990ba0ad0bc277a07fb5c705b833db","tid":1981304,"uid":165934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T14:54:29.000Z","msg":"談近來YouTuber之是非。<br />\n<br />\n幾年前，在我已經不再以YouTuber自居的時候。<br />\n<br />\n一位YouTube員工對我說：<br />\n<br />\n「為什麼香港沒有説網絡是非的Channel？明明YouTuber比明星更多曝光，但傳統娛樂版又不願意談YouTuber......分明就是個大市場呀！」<br />\n<br />\n沒錯，很多事情都有市場，能賺錢。<br />\n<br />\n但事情也有應為和不應為。<br />\n<br />\n而現時局勢，任誰也會同意，是非鬥爭不應為。<br />\n<br />\n然而在香港，香港人就是市場。<br />\n<br />\n這個市場口講不分化，但是會訂閲芷鹿泥馬；口説不割𥱊，但是又在連登説是非。<br />\n<br />\n現在打開YouTube，就會看到香港網絡忽然添了一堆説是非的影片丶説是非的小人。<br />\n<br />\n是非紛擾多如牛毛，又似雨後春筍。<br />\n<br />\n難道是大J和屎萊姆造就了這些是非嗎？<br />\n<br />\n難道不是那數以萬計的點撃人數嗎？<br />\n<br />\n市場置身事外，市場卻又煽風點火，結果卻是罪在YouTuber，我也是笑了。<br />\n<br />\n你們哪一個從沒推Post，又從沒看過是非影片的，就出來用石頭，扔死你們自造的神吧！<br />\n<br />\n我無所謂，反正我就是個無神論者。"},{"pid":"3848f83d2c4ae5ebfbf9411b67e40a5a14dcdd36","tid":1981304,"uid":165934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T14:54:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MCnzwGg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMCnzwGg.jpg&h=0a1c22fb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b8ac05a260878608f1418acf49c9d456acaa7120","tid":1981304,"uid":165934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T14:56:35.000Z","msg":"Hello youtube 我係Jason"},{"pid":"29ea1c61a88b6f949a38baa53d263a09c8858e66","tid":1981304,"uid":165934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T14:56:50.000Z","msg":"大家好，我係屎萊姆"},{"pid":"eef8677e9feca88261da3858d22985d1ec43211a","tid":1981304,"uid":165934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T15:10:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a83e926fccfb262a66b1c91ee9ef0db80d7dafe","tid":1981304,"uid":339272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29ea1c61a88b6f949a38baa53d263a09c8858e66","tid":1981304,"uid":165934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T14:56:50.000Z","msg":"大家好，我係屎萊姆"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T15:17:46.000Z","msg":"大家好，我係屎來母個fd細b哥"}]}